OL,4,Cworking week on employers
OL,6,FLabour says there is nothing
OL,7,Fcompulsory about their proposed plans
OL,8,Fand they will allow workers more
OL,9,Fflexibility, as ITV News Political
OL,10,FCorrespondent Libby Wiener reports
OL,12,FThe government has denied it will
OL,13,Fforce businesses to allow staff to
OL,14,Fwork a four-day week, following
OL,15,Freports it is considering giving them
OL,16,Fthe power to condense employees' hours.
OL,18,FMinisters have insisted they will not
OL,19,F"impose" the change on employers, amid
OL,20,Freports the plans are set to be
OL,21,Fannounced in the autumn.
