OL,6,FEducation minister Baroness Jacqui
OL,7,FSmith told ITV News the plans were
OL,8,Fabout giving workers more flexibility,
OL,9,Fwhich in turn boosts productivity.
OL,11,F"The four-day week idea is not saying,
OL,12,F'okay I'm only going to work four-
